headline: Synchrony's CareCredit Offered at 100% of Public Veterinary University Hospitals Nationwide, Expanding Access to Pet Care
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF), a premier consumer financial services company, today announced that its CareCredit health and wellness credit card has been named the preferred financing partner for the Texas A&M University Veterinary Medical Teaching Hospital. This collaboration marks a significant milestone for CareCredit, solidifying its presence in all 29 public veterinary university hospitals in the country.
